1. Seperate DB models and pydantic models
2. db models should go into db/models/db_models.py (make sure you create a db/__init__.py file)
3. pydantic models should go into db/models/pydantic_models.py (make sure you create a db/models/__init__.py file)
4. Use SQLalchemy and replace the sessions
5. Database configurations should go into db/configs.py
6. Study about __init__.py file and why it should be created
7. Check whether everything works
8. Slowly add validations in the routes
9. Try to configure debugger for fastapi